dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile is an index to the 2010 aerial survey of the Stanford University Campus.  Air Flight Services. (2019). Stanford Campus 2010, Index Map. Stanford Digital Repository. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/qb865wf0229 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
